<F P=100> TURKEY </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Terrorist' Killed; 61 Captured in Southeast </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA3101195594 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 
GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA3101195594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over still of regional map] </F>
  [Text] One terrorist has been killed in operations carried 
out by the security forces in the Kocadagi region of 
Diyarbakir's Kulp District. A total of 57 persons abetting the 
terrorist organization and trying to get organized in the state 
of emergency region have been captured. 
  Two terrorists and two abettors have been captured in 
Malatya. According to a statement issued by the Malatya 
Governor's Office, three Kalashnikovs, three hand grenades, and 
organizational documents have been seized. 

