<H3> <TI>   Defense Minister Holds Talks With France's Leotard </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3101160994 Bern Swiss Radio International in English 1500 
GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD3101160994 </F>
<F P=104>  Bern Swiss Radio International </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The French Defense Minister Francois Leotard has 
held talks in Switzerland with his Swiss counterpart Kaspar 
Villiger. Mr. Leotard briefed Mr. Villiger on France's United 
Nations involvement in Bosnia in reference to possible Swiss 
participation in future UN peacekeeping operations. 
  The French minister also said he was concerned about 
Bosnia's 
warring factions mobilizing for an all-out war and reiterated 
that he favored protective air strikes. 

</TEXT>

