<H3> <TI>   Syrian Labor Minister Arrives for Visit, Talks </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  NC0202212594 Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network in Greek 2000 GMT 2 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0202212594 </F>
<F P=104>  Nicosia Cyprus Broadcasting Corporation Radio 
Network </F>



<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Greek </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Syrian Social Affairs and Labor Minister 'Ali Khalil 
arrived in Cyprus this evening for an official visit. The 
Syrian minister will hold talks with Labor and Social Insurance 
Minister Andreas Mousiouttas to improve the cooperation between 
the two countries in the areas of responsibility of the two 
ministries. At the same time, there will be negotiations for a 
social insurance agreement between the two countries. During 
his visit to Cyprus, Khalil will be received by President 
Glavkos Kliridhis. He will also meet House of Representatives 
President Alexis Galanos and other officials. 

</TEXT>

